Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: kevin
Version: 0.6
Summary: Self-hostable continuous integration toolkit
Home-page: https://github.com/SFTtech/kevin
Author: SFT Technologies
Author-email: jj@stusta.net
License: AGPL3+
Description: Components for running a continuous integration service right on your own servers.
        Kevin interacts with the Internet, falk manages the virtual machines and containers, chantal executes your build jobs.
        
        It's designed to interact with a code hosting platform like GitHub but can easily be extended for others.
        Pull requests are build in temporary containers that are deletedafter execution.
Platform: Linux
